header.gameNote: HALL OF FAME CLASSIC - CAMPUS GAME

videos.description: Prince Ali makes a clutch steal, jukes pass a defender, but misses what would be a monster dunk.
videos.headline: Ali barely misses the statement slam

videos.description: Jaylen Hands takes the ball from beyond half court and puts the moves on Central Arkansas defenders for the layup.
videos.headline: Hands with the stylish layup

videos.description: Jordan Howard takes the pass from Deandre Jones and shoots from deep.  The ball bounces upward off the rim and falls right back in the basket.
videos.headline: Howard's deep three takes a lucky bounce

videos.description: Jaylen Hands moves down the court on the fast break and tosses it up to Kris Wilkes for the slam dunk
videos.headline: Hands finds Wilkes for early alley-oop

videos.description: Hayden Koval blocks the shot of Thomas Welsh. The ball is then quickly played down the court to Jordan Howard who makes the fast-break layup and narrows the UCLA lead to two.
videos.headline: Koval's clutch block leads to points

videos.description: Central Arkansas' Jordan Howard takes matters into his own hands and pops a three-pointer from deep to close the gap on UCLA's lead.
videos.headline: Howard's deep three cuts UCLA lead to 2

videos.description: Jordan Howard drives into the lane while tossing up a high shot which bounces in off the backboard to tie the score.
videos.headline: Howard's ridiculous lob shot ties the score for Central Arkansas

videos.description: After a costly UCLA turnover, Kris Wilkes runs back on defense to block Central Arkansas's 2-point attempt.
videos.headline: Wilkes amends UCLA turnover with clutch block

videos.description: Deandre Jones inbounds the pass to Jordan Howard who hits a clutch 3-point jumper which would eventually lead to a tied score at the end of regulation.
videos.headline: Howard helps send Central Arkansas to overtime

videos.description: Jordan Howard takes the pass from Hayden Koval and drains the deep three-pointer while getting fouled. He then hits his free throw earning a clutch 4-point play in OT.
videos.headline: Howard earns a 4-point play for Central Arkansas
